  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Advice on net-zero energy challenges
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  

  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Advice to the Minister for Business, Energy and Clean Growth, to summarise briefing sessions on retrofitting to decarbonise homes and developing a hydrogen economy.   </p>

  </div>
</div>

